# Project-level MCP wiring — port lives in user-data/config/config.json,
# so it's per-user. Kept locally to survive ~/.claude.json races from
# concurrent agent sessions (see RUNBOOK.md "mcp.wiring_*" invariants).
.mcp.json
# Auto-generated workspace-local agent context (current state, jobs list,
# integrations, personality). Regenerated hourly by refresh-claude-md;
# Claude Code / Gemini auto-load `*.local.md` alongside the tracked
# CLAUDE.md / GEMINI.md so this never enters git.
CLAUDE.local.md
GEMINI.local.md
# Local CLI scratch — surreal SQL history, paste-in api key files, etc.
history.txt
*.apikey
geminapikey
# Scratch dir used by polish-* loops for intermediate work-product (audit
# seeds, orphan lists, fixtures-to-rotate). Never reviewed in PRs.
tmp/
# aider AI assistant cache (chat history, input history, ctags). Recreated
# on next aider run if used; deleting is safe.
.aider*
# pnpm-only: prevent accidental commit of an npm-generated lockfile.
# Belt-and-suspenders with `package-lock=false` in .npmrc.
package-lock.json
